Upstream-Source: <URL:http://adabroker.eu.org/distrib/adabroker-0.9.tar.gz>
Home-Page: <URL:http://adabroker.eu.org/>
Description: CORBA ORB in Ada 95 and IDL-to-Ada 95 compiler.
Packaged-For: Debian
