Major-Changes:
 None.
Build-Depends: gnat, g++
Build: sh
 make
Clean: sh
 make clean || true

Package: adabroker
Architecture: any
Depends: [/usr/bin/*]
Description: AdaBroker binary package.
 This package contains the adabroker IDL-to-Ada compiler, and
 the Broca runtime-library (the AdaBroker ORB).
Install: sh
 yada install -bin adabroker/adabroker -as adabroker
 yada undocumented adabroker.1
 yada install -data -into /usr/lib/adabroker src/*.ad? src/*.ad? src/*.ali src/libbroca.a
Postinst: sh
 chmod a-w /usr/lib/adabroker/*.ali
